quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,24,Mbega warashikiwe n’inkuru z’abashitsi b’iteka b’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  51,25,"Mugihe binjira munzu yiwe bavuga bati:- Amahoro y’Imana abe kuri wewe ntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) nawe abishura ati:- Amahoro y’Imana abe kuri mwebwe bashitsi ntamenye"
  51,26,Mukanya aca agenda murugo iwe no kumutambukanyi wiwe arabazimana intama nziza inuze
  51,27,"Arabashikiriza hafi y’abo n’ukuvuga ati:- mbega ko muda fungura"
  51,28,"Aca abagirira ko amakenga, nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntutinye, nabo baca bamushikiriza inkuru nziza z’ikibondo gifise ubumenyi buhagije"
  51,29,"Ninaho umunega w’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) y’aba tumbera nawe avuga yikubita mumaso n’igitangaro cinshi avuga ati:- umukecuru nkanje kandi w’ingumba nzo vyara"
  51,30,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- egome, nuko nyene n’uko Umuremyi wawe yabivuze, mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo nyene ubuhizi ifise n’ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  51,31,"Yavuze ati:- none ivyipfuzo vyanyu n’ibihe mwebwe mwarungitswe"
  51,32,"Nabo bishura bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarungitswe kugira ngo tugende guhonya b’abantu babi"
  51,33,Kugira ngo tubajugunyire ko iminana y’ivyondo vy’umuriro
  51,34,Yashizwe ko ibimenyetso n’Umuremyi wawe kubera abo bantu barenze imbibe z’Imana kubijanye n’ibicumuro vyabo
  51,35,"Kubera ivyo, twakuye mwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bari muri ico gisagara"
  51,36,Mugabo ntitwahasanze muri ico gisagara atari inzu imwe y’aba Isilamu
  51,37,Dusigamwo ikimenyetso kuri bamwe batinya ibihano bibabaza
  51,38,"No\tkunkuru\ty’intumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tigihe\ttwamutwara\tkwa Fir’auni dufise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro"
  51,39,"Mugabo\tyarahakanye\tkubera\tubushobozi\tbwiwe\tn’ukuvuga\tati:-\tuyu muntu n’umurozi canke n’umusazi"
  51,40,"Duca\tturamufata\thamwe\tn’ingabo\tziwe\tn’ukuba\tjugunya\tmukiyaga, kandi nawe atabwa ko n’umwikomo"
  51,41,"No\tkunkuru\ty’intumwa\ty’Imana\tAadi\t(iii)\tmugihe\ttwaba\trungikira umuyaga ukaze cane w’ukubahonya"
  51,42,"Ntiwa\tsigaza\tikintu\ticarico\tcose\tcawushikiye,\tahubwo\tcawugize nk’umugozi uhoyahoya"
  51,43,"N’inkuru\tzabo\tkwa\tThamuda\tmugihe\tbavuga\tbati:-\tni\tmwinezereze kugihe kigufiya gusa"
  51,44,"Barahakana\titegeko\try’Umuremyi\twabo,\tmukanya\tisase\tumucanwa w’inkuba niwo wasokoye imitima yabo nabo bibonera"
  51,45,Nti bashoboye guhagarara canke nti bashoboye kwirwanako
  51,46,"N’abantu\tb’intumwa\ty’Imana\tNuhu\t(iii)\tnabone\timbere\tyabo,\tmu vy’ukuri bari mu bantu b’abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"